1
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,760
You made me look so fat.

2
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,079
I'm obviously skinny.

3
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,359
What a bunch of idiots.

4
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,719
How am I supposed to pick?

5
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:36,879
Perfect timing.

6
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:39,120
Which photo should we leak?

7
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,719
I don't care. You decide.

8
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:43,359
You're so pathetic.

9
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,480
The second floor's on fire!

10
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,599
What's going on?

11
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,840
How could the second floor catch fire?

12
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,719
Hurry, hurry, go!

13
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:55,359
Wait!

14
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,439
Where are you going?

15
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:57,200
Where are you going?

16
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,239
The Key of Fate is still in there.

17
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:59,840
Which matters more, the Key or your life?

18
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,519
Go, go, go!

19
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,239
If the Key of Fate melts...

20
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:03,079
We're finished.

21
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,159
Let's get out alive first!

22
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:04,879
I'll get it back for you.

23
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,120
Don't worry.

24
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,840
I'll definitely get it back for you.

25
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,479
In the corner of the sofa on the second floor.

26
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:13,879
Zhang Xiaobei.

27
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,400
Be careful.

28
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,000
Are you okay?

29
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:49,120
Here.

30
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,400
Take it.

31
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,800
Your Key of Fate.

32
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,840
So you kept it on you the whole time.

33
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,199
If you hadn't...

34
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,680
...given me the Key of Fate you found,

35
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:12,000
I wouldn't have given you the real Key of Fate.

36
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,960
After all, we're Partners for life.

37
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,520
Honesty matters, doesn't it?

38
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:19,000
Weren't you just worried...

39
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,520
...that after I took the Key of Fate...

40
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,840
...I'd ruin the engagement?

41
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:23,159
No need.

42
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,599
I only ever planned to...

43
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:26,039
...swap identities for 30 days.

44
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:28,520
Once you become the Sheng family's bride,

45
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:29,840
then I could...

46
00:03:30,039 --> 00:03:32,000
...be with Siqi without any obstacles.

47
00:03:34,159 --> 00:03:35,039
Thirty days.

48
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:37,360
After tasting Sheng Yuanzhou's life,

49
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,400
do you think...

50
00:03:38,439 --> 00:03:40,280
you can go back to Commoners' Alley?

51
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,439
Not everyone is like you,

52
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:44,400
heartless enough to abandon their parents.

53
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,599
It is easy to go from frugal to lavish,

54
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,960
but hard to go from lavish back to frugal.

55
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,680
We'll see.

56
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:57,240
I won't easily give up Siqi or my parents.

57
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,479
I hope you...

58
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,719
...treat...

59
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:03,000
the real Sheng Yuanzhou well.

60
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:13,360
Welcome to "Xiaohei Tells You the Truth."

61
00:04:13,599 --> 00:04:14,599
The Prosperity Group's young master

62
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:16,720
was actually seduced by a pretty face?

63
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,879
With his engagement just around the corner,

64
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:20,639
Wanli Construction's heiress controls him.

65
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:22,480
Romantic dates, wet T-shirt parties,

66
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:24,639
they really know how to get wild.

67
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:26,399
Is it human nature sinking...

68
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,120
...or morality collapsing...

69
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,879
The kids have minds of their own.

70
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,439
There's nothing I can do.

71
00:04:38,759 --> 00:04:40,279
Kids these days,

72
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,399
no one can control them.

73
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:44,240
They insist on "marriage freedom," right?

74
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,040
Sheng Shizhong.

75
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,879
So you're gonna kick away the ladder.

76
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:52,319
Lin Chengren.

77
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:55,480
I've helped you enough all these years.

78
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:56,839
Otherwise, how would Benevolence Hospital

79
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:58,480
have expanded to this scale?

80
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,680
And your Cancer Center.

81
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,959
That investment money, for you,

82
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:04,240
was a lifesaver, wasn't it?

83
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,000
Mr. Sheng.

84
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,439
Don't forget

85
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,839
why we made

86
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:15,079
this engagement back then.

87
00:05:18,199 --> 00:05:20,000
You're bringing up the past to...

88
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,000
threaten me.

89
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,800
I'm not threatening you.

90
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:31,279
I really do have proof of that.

91
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,160
It's been over ten years.

92
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:37,600
You've never mentioned it once.

93
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:45,160
If I dare sit at this table,

94
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,600
I've got a strong hand.

95
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:49,600
Let the kids get married,

96
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,079
and I'll keep that secret

97
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:57,680
buried with me.

98
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:11,399
What's the Lins' connection to the Shengs?

99
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:16,360
Lin Chengren knows a lot of Sheng secrets.

100
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,199
Dad.

101
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,600
When did you get back?

102
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,319
You didn't even tell me.

103
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,480
I've been waiting for you forever.

104
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,319
I was thinking about some things.

105
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,480
Why do you look so exhausted?

106
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:30,959
Where did you go?

107
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,920
Did the Sheng family give you trouble?

108
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:34,399
No, no, no.

109
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:41,240
Siqi.

110
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,279
I would never

111
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:44,519
let you give up the Mrs. Sheng position

112
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:45,560
to someone else.

113
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:46,759
Dad.

114
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:49,560
I don't want to be Mrs. Sheng at all.

115
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:53,439
There's a lot you still don't understand.

116
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:56,399
But trust me, I would never hurt you.

117
00:06:56,399 --> 00:06:57,759
Our family's hospital

118
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,240
can't be left to you.

119
00:07:02,879 --> 00:07:04,199
So I have to

120
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:05,600
find you a good match.

121
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,399
Only then can I rest easy.

122
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:10,160
As for that poor kid...

123
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:13,319
he's not someone you can rely on.

124
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:14,600
But...

125
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,800
lately I've felt something's off too.

126
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,040
I feel like

127
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:22,439
a lot of things have changed.

128
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,839
It's like I...

129
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,759
don't want to be with Xiaobei that much.

130
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:30,879
You've grown up.

131
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:33,600
Have I?

132
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,279
About the recent rumors

133
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,120
between Ms. Jiang Lai and me,

134
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,040
I'm announcing here and now:

135
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:47,399
Ms. Jiang Lai

136
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:49,160
is my girlfriend.

137
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,439
So today, I also announce

138
00:07:53,439 --> 00:07:55,560
I'm officially breaking my engagement to Ms. Lin Siqi...

139
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,040
Wait.

140
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,920
What's she here for?

141
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,120
What kind of war zone is this?

142
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,279
Why's she here?

143
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:10,160
No idea.

144
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,360
Is she here to win him back?

145
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:17,199
Sheng Yuanzhou, putting on a show here?

146
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:18,439
And you didn't even invite me?

147
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:22,199
Lin Siqi, we're all adults.

148
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:23,279
We can make a clean break.

149
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,240
Fine.

150
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,040
Then let's make a clean break.

151
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:32,480
I, Lin Siqi, officially announce

152
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:34,600
I am ending my engagement with the Shengs.

153
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:40,919
Oh my God.

154
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,120
That's so badass.

155
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,159
Dumping him like a boss.

156
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,200
Starting today,

157
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:48,840
I, Lin Siqi, and Sheng Yuanzhou

158
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:51,039
are no longer engaged.

159
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:53,000
We can each marry whoever we want.

160
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,159
Sheng Yuanzhou.

161
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:03,000
I won't let my dad

162
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,039
because of this,

163
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:04,840
keep bowing to your family

164
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,440
again and again.

165
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:08,159
So get this straight:

166
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:11,039
I'm the one who ended the engagement

167
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:12,600
and chose love.

168
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:20,919
Why'd she leave?

169
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:29,440
No clue if you're doing this for yourself,

170
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,000
or making it easy for someone else.

171
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:34,000
She's running to the real Sheng Yuanzhou now.

172
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,759
I hereby officially announce

173
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,360
my engagement to Ms. Jiang Lai.

174
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,519
Help!

175
00:09:51,759 --> 00:09:52,399
What happened?

176
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,320
Why'd he leave?

177
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,039
Dad!

178
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,440
Dad!

179
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,559
Call an ambulance, now!

180
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:58,519
The doctor said

181
00:10:59,039 --> 00:11:00,600
Dad had a sudden heart attack.

182
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,919
He didn't take his meds in time,

183
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,840
so he fell down the stairs.

184
00:11:04,279 --> 00:11:05,320
He hit his head

185
00:11:05,759 --> 00:11:06,759
and had a cerebral hemorrhage.

186
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,360
They've cleared the clot,

187
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:10,799
but when he'll wake up

188
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,759
is still uncertain.

189
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:14,840
Honey...

190
00:11:16,159 --> 00:11:18,639
You have to wake up.

191
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:21,120
If you leave us like this,

192
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:23,440
what are we supposed to do, honey?

193
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,240
It's okay.

194
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,840
Don't be too upset.

195
00:11:27,279 --> 00:11:28,600
Dad will wake up for sure.

196
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:32,799
This is all your fault!

197
00:11:34,399 --> 00:11:35,600
If you hadn't called off the engagement,

198
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,240
he wouldn't have gone there and fallen.

199
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,200
If anything happens to Lin,

200
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,120
I'll never forgive you!

201
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,559
You're the murderer!

202
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,720
Don't do this, don't do this.

203
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,919
This has nothing to do with him.

204
00:11:44,159 --> 00:11:45,679
Do you have any conscience at all?

205
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,519
Your dad got hurt like this because of you,

206
00:11:47,519 --> 00:11:49,000
and you're siding with outsiders!

207
00:11:49,559 --> 00:11:51,279
This has nothing to do with Siqi.

208
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,080
If you want someone to blame, blame me.

209
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,360
Now you know how to care about her?

210
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,120
Then why did you call it off back then?

211
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:05,879
Thanks for today.

212
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,120
This matter

213
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:10,519
isn't your fault.

214
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:15,879
If you ever need help,

215
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,440
just tell me.

216
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:23,519
But...

217
00:12:24,799 --> 00:12:26,559
Dad clearly took his meds with him that day.

218
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:28,559
So why didn't he take them in time?

219
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,440
The back corridor cameras were under repair.

220
00:12:37,759 --> 00:12:39,159
They did find at the bottom of the stairwell

221
00:12:39,159 --> 00:12:40,200
a scattered pill box.

222
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,679
But it was handed to the police that day.

223
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:42,759
Got it.

224
00:12:52,639 --> 00:12:54,840
Lin Chengren had a sudden heart attack.

225
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,279
He took out the pill box,

226
00:12:59,679 --> 00:13:00,759
but it slipped from his hand.

227
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,919
The pill box fell from midway up the stairs

228
00:13:02,919 --> 00:13:03,879
straight down to the bottom.

229
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,399
Lin Chengren tried to grab the pill box,

230
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:09,159
but he twisted his ankle and tumbled down.

231
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,200
But why was he in the stairwell?

232
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,240
Was he meeting someone?

233
00:13:26,879 --> 00:13:27,960
What are you doing?

234
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,759
How can you, right in front of my dad,

235
00:13:35,759 --> 00:13:36,879
do something like this?

236
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:39,840
Your dad can't see us anyway.

237
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,399
Do you have no shame?

238
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,960
Who taught you to mouth off to your elders?

239
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,000
Elder?

240
00:13:45,519 --> 00:13:46,320
You don't deserve that.

241
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,840
Whether you like it or not,

242
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,200
I'm still your stepmother.

243
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,080
I'm your mother in name.

244
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:52,879
You don't deserve to be.

245
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,039
Don't be so hot-headed.

246
00:13:55,039 --> 00:13:56,159
Get the hell out!

247
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:58,200
You should go first.

248
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:05,080
Do you have any conscience?

249
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:06,919
My dad is lying here right now,

250
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,919
in a coma, and we don't know his condition.

251
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,840
How could you do this?

252
00:14:11,759 --> 00:14:12,600
What did I do?

253
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,639
Watch your mouth.

254
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:16,360
With your dad like this,

255
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:18,320
do you think he can divorce me,

256
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,879
or can you kick me out?

257
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,840
True, I can't do anything to you.

258
00:14:23,639 --> 00:14:25,240
But you should have a conscience.

259
00:14:25,759 --> 00:14:26,879
Conscience?

260
00:14:26,879 --> 00:14:27,919
What's that supposed to be?

261
00:14:28,279 --> 00:14:29,519
Can you eat it,

262
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,919
or spend it like money?

263
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,519
Who was that man just now?

264
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:37,960
Oh, right.

265
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,799
I was just about to tell you.

266
00:14:39,799 --> 00:14:41,679
He's Benevolence Hospital's future Director,

267
00:14:41,679 --> 00:14:42,559
named Jiang Min.

268
00:14:42,559 --> 00:14:44,519
The shareholders' meeting will announce it soon.

269
00:14:45,279 --> 00:14:47,960
You're making your lover the Director?

270
00:14:49,039 --> 00:14:50,200
Who gave you that right?

271
00:14:51,399 --> 00:14:52,200
Siqi.

272
00:14:52,679 --> 00:14:54,440
Aren't you mistaken about something?

273
00:14:54,799 --> 00:14:56,440
Your dad has fallen ill.

274
00:14:57,120 --> 00:15:00,080
I now hold all his share exercise rights.

275
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,480
I

276
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:05,440
am now Benevolence Hospital's biggest shareholder.
